text:
This is located at pioneer sector.
It is situation around an industrial zone.

The coffeeshop is huge and there are quite many food stalls here.

Tried the fried noodles here (SL economical Beehoon). Not too bad. Comparable to normal coffeeshops.
Has its own carpark but limited.

The place is dirty and the service attitude is poor. Where can I go?
